{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_01","textHome":"我是七濑幸佳，在水名女子学园上学的高中一@年级生。放学后偷偷去游戏中心算是兴趣吧@？啊，还是请当做没听到吧。因为对班里的@朋友保密……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":301700,"motion":300}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_17","textHome":"其实，最近我沉迷于游戏中心角落里布满灰尘@的弹球……啊，拜托对我的朋友保密。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_18","textHome":"水名女子学园和圣莉莉安娜学园的区别吗？说@起来……水名是正宗的的传统学校，莉莉安@娜是名流大小姐学校！这样的感觉吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_19","textHome":"看到了！这是胜利的预兆！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_20","textHome":"现在我的力量，就算是麻烦事也欢迎哦！……@假的啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_21","textHome":"魔法少女也会一点一点成长呢。 呃……但是@该不会实力变得越强，麻烦事的等级也会提@高吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_22","textHome":"成为魔法少女后，稍微变得坚强了一点……我@明白了一件事。被逼入绝境，可能要死了！@当有这样的觉悟，无论如何也想要活下去的@时候……才更能感受到自己还活着的感觉。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_23","textHome":"因为变强了，确实看清了一些事情……但是，@有时也会想，一直这样生活下去真的好吗？@魔法少女能做的事，不是还有别的吗……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_24","textHome":"对不起！不，是想在给您添麻烦之前先道歉！@今天一定不要卷入奇怪的事件中，希望能平@安度过这一天。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_25","textHome":"早起更好。要是一直这样睡下去，不醒过来的@话父母会担心得把我送去医院的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_26","textHome":"中午的时候不紧张吗？我会紧张。虽然和朋友@们一起吃午饭很开心，但是会因为我而卷入@混乱中的样子……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_02","textHome":"每次都会引起混乱。我叫七濑幸佳。因为某些@原因是很容易被卷入混乱的体质，所以建议@马上离我远点……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_27","textHome":"请等一下。到了关键时间了。什么？我在说奖@牌游戏哦！这里正是分出胜负的时候！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":400}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_28","textHome":"唔哇……今天要是能香甜地睡上一觉就好了。@因为最近就连在梦里也被卷入麻烦之中了…@…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_29","textHome":"啊，难道是麻烦的事情吗？以我为中心半径2@米内，请不要把麻烦事带进来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_30","textHome":"击退魔女……确实是既紧张又恐怖，但我并不@讨厌。在变成魔法少女之前我都不知道竟然@有这样的世界存在。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_31","textHome":"会复制魔法少女的屋子？那是100%会有麻@烦事的地方吧？去那里不是自投罗网吗！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":400}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_32","textHome":"是魔法少女小队战吗？……我可以参加吗？会@不会给小队的各位带来灾难呢……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_33","textHome":"啊……没注意到对不起。刚才在学习。那个…@…能不能不要露出意外的表情？在学校要说@起来也算是优等生啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_34","textHome":"最近买了智能手机，很近的最近。偶尔也会放@松一下玩游戏。奖、奖牌游戏之类的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_35","textHome":"我没有什么特长。小的时候虽然学过钢琴和小@提琴，但水平不上不下，最后还是渐渐淡忘@了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_36","textHome":"呜……我魔法少女的样子……谁看都知道是最@爱奖牌游戏的女孩子吧！……本来应该是少@女的秘密兴趣的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":301700,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_03","textHome":"虽然很想当做没看见……"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_37","textHome":"我和圣莉莉安娜学园的同学们还是有很多交流@的哦。当中也有着在宅邸里有很多执事和女@仆的超级大小姐的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":301700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_38","textHome":"步鸟是个总会拼尽全力的好孩子呢。我觉得我@很理解妹妹理音想独占她的心情。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3017_00_39","textHome":"论没存在感的话我很有自信的哦。明明在学校@遇见过好多次明槻前辈，却连我是黑羽都没@有意识到，这种程度。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_